    <h1><a href="/news/General-Tech/Podcast-337-Snapdragon-810-Preview-USB-31-Dell-Venue-8-Tablet-and-more">Podcast #337 - Snapdragon 810 Preview, USB 3.1, Dell Venue 8 Tablet and more!</a></h1>
    <h2>Subject: <a href="/subject/general-tech">General Tech</a> | February 19, 2015 - 02:22 PM | <a href="/users/Ken-Addison" rel="author">Ken Addison</a><br />
     Tagged: <a href="/category/tags/podcast">podcast</a>, <a href="/category/tags/video">video</a>, <a href="/category/tags/snapdragon">snapdragon</a>, <a href="/category/tags/qualcomm">qualcomm</a>, <a href="/category/tags/810">810</a>, <a href="/category/tags/usb-3.1">usb 3.1</a>, <a href="/category/tags/x99a-gaming-9-ack">x99a gaming 9 ack</a>, <a href="/category/tags/dell">dell</a>, <a href="/category/tags/venue-8-7000">venue 8 7000</a>, <a href="/category/tags/crucial-bx100">crucial bx100</a>, <a href="/category/tags/bx-100">bx 100</a>, <a href="/category/tags/silicon-motion">silicon motion</a>, <a href="/category/tags/corsair">corsair</a>, <a href="/category/tags/cs850m">CS850M</a>, <a href="/category/tags/nvidia">nvidia</a>, <a href="/category/tags/amd">amd</a>, <a href="/category/tags/intel">Intel</a></h2>
