<td>16GB eMMC<br />
			MicroSD Slot (up to 512GB)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Camera</td>
<td>8MP Rear + Dual 720p Depth<br />
			2MP Front</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Wireless</td>
