  <ul class="links inline"><li class="node_read_more first"><a href="/reviews/Storage/Crucial-BX100-250-and-500GB-SATA-SSD-Review-Silicon-Motion-Returns" title="Read the rest of Crucial BX100 250 and 500GB SATA SSD Review - Silicon Motion Returns.">Read more</a></li>
<li class="comment_add last"><a href="/reviews/Storage/Crucial-BX100-250-and-500GB-SATA-SSD-Review-Silicon-Motion-Returns#comments" title="Jump to the first comment of this posting">Comments (6)</a></li>
</ul>
